data.description: BETTER ACT FAST ON THIS ONE-OF-A-KIND, LAKEVIEW HOME IN A POPULAR GATED COMMUNITY! Enjoy nightly sunsets with an incomparable view of the pristine Johns Lake with this luxury two-story home. With a wide range of upgrades and enhancements throughout almost 5,000 square feet of living space, this gorgeous home provides space for everyone in the family including a conversation room with custom woodwork, large dining room and and a spacious family room, all with attractive, dark wood framing and ceiling beams. The open floor plan looks out to the custom, infinity pool and spa with spectacular fire bowls, custom lighting and a phenomenal lake view. Your backyard oasis is perfect for relaxing or entertaining friends with its shellock pavered (heat resistant) lanai, stonework pillars, outdoor fireplace with seating area and high-end outdoor kitchen featuring custom cabinetry, an inviting island bar, flat top and gas grill, dual tap kegerator, refrigerator and ice machine. The backyard retreat also boasts professionally designed landscaping, an outdoor lighting package and your own boat dock equipped with electric, water and two floating jet ski spaces. The gourmet kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, 42-inch cabinets, a custom range hood, subway tile backsplash, walk-in pantry and an oversized waterfall quartz island and plenty of storage. The first floor also features a guest suite complete with full bath. Upstairs you’ll find a large bonus room with wet bar, media room with projector and screen, home office and three additional bedrooms with walk-in closets. The owners suite features a tray ceiling, two walk-in closets and primary bathroom with separate vanities, granite countertops, garden tub and separate shower plus a balcony that stretches along the entire back of the home with an incredible view of the pool and lake.  Additional upgrades include luxury vinyl flooring throughout first floor and second floor common areas, pavered driveway and sidewalk, crown moulding throughout, wood paneled ceilings on front and back porch, water softener, three-car tandem garage and recent exterior paint. Hickory Hammock is a gated neighborhood the best of Florida living, a resort-style pool with a multi-function clubhouse, volleyball courts, tennis courts, workout facility, community dock, playground, dog park and a walking trail. Low HOA dues and A schools make this home better than all the rest. Conveniently located to downtown Winter Garden, Fowler's Grove shopping and major highways. This home has it all, better act fast on this truly special home!
